ItemDesc: Terrifying tusks left behind during the borisin conquests. Used to level up Traces significantly for <color=#f29e38ff>Destruction</color> characters.
ItemBGDesc: Borisin can further enhance their bodies through their innate "Moon Rage." The battle-frenzied warriors exhibit incredible healing abilities, shedding the blood of their enemies in a sanguine mist together with the unbridled growth of their muscles and bones. "O, Brood Lord, grant us divine strength."
